os </PERSON> said <PERSON> Shultz </PERSON> promised to expedite the delivery of <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> military equipment to the <LOCATION> Philippine </LOCATION> military. The <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION> this year provided more than $ 85 million in military help.
