rs away in handcuffs, crack dealers are operating with impunity on the same block,'' said <PERSON> Sliwa </PERSON>. Vendors whose carts are confiscated face up to a $ 1,000 fine. Recovering the carts will cost $ 65 plus a $ 5-a-day storage fee.
