<FIRST>u p AM-Bentsen-Senate     07-12 0445</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Bentsen-Senate,430</SECOND>
<HEAD>`LBJ Law' Allows Dual Candidacies for Bentsen</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Political Rdp Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By KEN HERMAN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>AUSTIN, Texas (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
