<HEAD>State Department Rejects Two Gorbachev Proposals</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By BARRY SCHWEID</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>AP Diplomatic Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>KASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
