<PERSON> D. </PERSON> <PERSON> Roosevelt </PERSON>'s proposal to enlarge the <ORGANIZATION> Supreme </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Court </ORGANIZATION> In 1942, gasoline rationing began in the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION> during World War II. In 1943, Allied forces captured <PERSON> Palermo </PERSON>, <LOCATION> Sicily </LOCATION>. In 1975, the <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Representatives </ORGANIZATION> joined the <ORGANIZATION> Senate </ORGANIZATION> in voting to restore the American citizenship of Confederate Gen. <PERSON> Robert </PERSON> <PERSON> E. </PERSON> <PERSON> Lee </PERSON>, more than a century after his death. In 1981, Turkish terrorist <PERSON> Mehmet </PERSON> <PERSON> Ali </PERSON> <PERSON> Agca </PERSON> was sentenced in a <LOCATION> Rome </LOCATION> court to life in prison for shooting Pope <PERSON> John </PERSON> <PERSON> Paul </PERSON> II. In 1986, for the first time in half a century, the <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Representatives </ORGANIZATION> impeached a federal official. Judge <PERSON> Harry </PERSON> <PERSON> E. </PERSON> <PERSON> Claiborne </PERSON> was later convicted by the <ORGANIZATION> Senate </ORGANIZATION> of tax evasion and bringing disrepute on the federal courts. Ten years ago: President <PERSON> Anwar </PERSON> <PERSON> Sadat </PERSON> of <LOCATION> Egypt </LOCATION> delivered a speech in which he said the only obstacle to <LOCATION> Middle </LOCATION> <LOCATION> East </LOCATION> peace was what he termed the `` expansionist ambitions'' of <LOCATION> Israeli </LOCATION> Prime Minister <PERSON> Menachem </PERSON> <PERSON> Begin </PERSON>. Five years ago: Clicking her heels like <PERSON> Dorothy </PERSON> in `` The Wizard of Oz'' and sighing, `` There's no place like home,'' <PERSON> Samanatha </PERSON> <PERSON> Smith </PERSON> returned with her parents to their house in <LOCATION> Ma